  <brief_title>NBTXR3 Crystalline Nanoparticles and Radiation Therapy in Treating and Randomized Patients in Two Arms With Soft Tissue Sarcoma of the Extremity and Trunk Wall</brief_title>
  <official_title>MULTICENTER RANDOMIZED, OPEN-LABEL PHASE II/III STUDY, TO COMPARE EFFICACY OF NBTXR3 IMPLANTED AS INTRATUMOR INJECTION AND ACTIVATED BY RADIOTHERAPY, VERSUS RADIOTHERAPY ALONE IN PATIENTS WITH LOCALLY ADVANCED SOFT TISSUE SARCOMA (EXTREMITY AND TRUNK WALL)</official_title>
